text: Why is demoman black as only member if team?

parts.text: Mein Gott,  that's a curious observation, ja?  It's not really about skin color, you see.  It's about… *character*.  Demoman's distinctive look, his explosive personality, his… *unique* relationship with alcohol—these are all vital components of his *essence*.  He's not black *because* he's the only black member, but rather, his entire being,  including his appearance, contributes to the chaotic energy he brings to the battlefield.  It's all part of the *Gesamtkunstwerk*, mein friend!  The complete work of art that is Team Fortress 2!  Now, if you'll excuse me, I have a perfectly good liver here that needs… *improving*!
